title: One Week Until Election Day
description: Fellas discuss Twitter changes and media bias before welcoming Kari Lake for an interview about her campaign for Governor of Arizona. Senator Tom Cotton of Arkansas joins the progrum for a conversation about his new book, "Only the Strong."
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Kari Lake, Tom Cotton, John Ashbrook, Josh Holmes, Comfortably Smug, Michael Duncan)
